We recommended and the Local Chief Executive agreed to direct the Municipal Treasurer to:

require the business taxpayers to submit the Sworn Statement of Gross Sales or Receipts for the preceding calendar year or quarter; and Certified photocopy of Income Tax Returns (ITR) to be submitted on or before April 30 of each year to determine if deficiency in business tax previously collected exists;

